Chain_Info2_Token_Description1="FTM is the primary token on the <a href='https://fantom.foundation/' class='a-config' target='_blank'>Fantom</a> network, and is used for securing the network (as the main utility token) through staking, for governance, for payments, and for fees. With a total supply of 3.175 billion FTM tokens, FTM is available as native mainnet tokens, as ERC-20 tokens, and as BEP-2 tokens.<br><br>Our cross-chain bridge, cBridge, supports the cross-chain bridging of FTM <span><img class='describe-img' src='https://get.celer.app/cbridge-icons/FTM.png' alt=''/></span> between multiple chains with the fastest speeds, lowest costs, and most secure transactions available. The full name of this asset is Fantom and the ticker of this asset is FTM."

